{
  "stem": "2581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am just worried about the people, our people, and the people of the world should stop-- start fighting prejudice and hatred, prejudice and hatred.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because like the German priest [INAUDIBLE] said, if you don't do it for your fellow man, pretty soon you'll have to do it for yourself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there's no one left to help you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thank you for having patience to listen to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as you well know, and I realize it in everything that I said, that it's just the-- the scratch the top of what was-- there are certain things that you can't remember, certain things you don't want to remember.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the reason I did it, because for a long time I couldn't even talk about it, is simply I can't say all these things to our children.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't say all these things to our grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I said any little thing that I tried to our granddaughter, I'd know that it affected her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, she's very-- kids are very sensitive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are good people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They can't imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you are good, you cannot imagine that the next person could be so cruel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and I wouldn't want to hurt my grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I'm glad that one day when they'll be older, they'll be able to understand and see what happened to their grandparents and do everything possible that something like that shouldn't be repeated again.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
